languages.text: "Как самонадеянно и глупо. У тебя нет ничего, что могло бы удовлетворить меня, мон-кай".
"The presumption. The stupidity. You have nothing that could satisfy me, mon-keigh."
languages.original_text: "Как самонадеянно и глупо. У тебя нет ничего, что могло бы удовлетворить меня, мон-кай".

languages.text: 「思い上がるな。愚か者。貴様に私を満足させることはできない、モン＝ケイ」
languages.original_text: "The presumption. The stupidity. You have nothing that could satisfy me, mon-keigh."

traits.locale_text: 「思い上がるな。愚か者。貴様に私を満足させることはできない、モン＝ケイ」

languages.text: “何等无耻，何等愚蠢。你可付不起雇佣我的代价，猴子。”
languages.original_text: "The presumption. The stupidity. You have nothing that could satisfy me, mon-keigh."

traits.locale_text: “何等无耻，何等愚蠢。你可付不起雇佣我的代价，猴子。”

languages.text: « Quelle audace. Et quelle stupidité. Rien de ce que vous pourriez m'offrir ne pourrait me satisfaire, mon-keigh. »
languages.original_text: "The presumption. The stupidity. You have nothing that could satisfy me, mon-keigh."

traits.locale_text: « Quelle audace. Et quelle stupidité. Rien de ce que vous pourriez m'offrir ne pourrait me satisfaire, mon-keigh. »

languages.text: «Qué presuntuos{mf|o|a}. Qué imbécil. No tienes nada que pueda interesarme, mon-keigh».
languages.original_text: "The presumption. The stupidity. You have nothing that could satisfy me, mon-keigh."

traits.locale_text: «Qué presuntuos{mf|o|a}. Qué imbécil. No tienes nada que pueda interesarme, mon-keigh».

languages.text: "Diese Vermessenheit. Diese Dummheit. Ihr habt nichts, was mich befriedigen könnte, Chem-Pan-Sey."
languages.original_text: "The presumption. The stupidity. You have nothing that could satisfy me, mon-keigh."

traits.locale_text: "Diese Vermessenheit. Diese Dummheit. Ihr habt nichts, was mich befriedigen könnte, Chem-Pan-Sey."

languages.text: "Bu ne hadsizlik! Bu ne ahmaklık! Yapacağın hiçbir ödeme beni memnun edemez mon-keigh."
